<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For You 🌹</title>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700;900&family=Dancing+Script:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  /* --- GLOBAL STYLES & CRIMSON THEME --- */
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    background: #800020; /* Deep Burgundy / Crimson Wine Background */
    color: #fff5f6; /* Soft cream text */
    overflow-x: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .page {
    display: none;
    min-height: 100vh;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
    padding: 20px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .page.active {
    display: flex;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* --- 🔮 THE LIQUID GLASS TEXTURE ENGINE --- */
  .glass-box {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), 
                inset 0 1px 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    color: #fff5f6;
    padding: 30px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  /* --- GLOBAL INTERACTIVE BUTTONS --- */
  .play-btn, .next-btn, .action-btn {
    display: block;
    margin: 20px auto 0 auto;
    padding: 12px 40px;
    background: #fff5f6;
    color: #800020;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 25px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .play-btn:hover, .next-btn:hover, .action-btn:hover { background: #ffccd5; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* --- PAGE 1: LOCK GATE LAYOUT --- */
  #page1 { flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .p1-left, .p1-right { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .glass-polaroid {
    position: relative;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); backdrop-filter: blur(15px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25); padding: 16px 16px 45px 16px; border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); width: 55%; max-width: 320px; transform: rotate(-2deg);
  }
  .glass-polaroid img { width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 6px; display: block; }
  .lock-screen-title { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: 600; }
  .lock-screen-subtitle { font-size: 1rem; color: #ffccd5; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .passcode-display {
    width: 200px; height: 50px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); border: 2px solid #ffccd5;
    border-radius: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.8rem; letter-spacing: 8px; margin-bottom: 25px;
  }
  .keypad { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 15px; max-width: 260px; }
  .key {
    width: 70px; height: 70px; background: #fff5f6; border: 2px solid #ffccd5; border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #800020; cursor: pointer; display: flex;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.2s ease; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }
  .key:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
  .key.action-key { font-size: 1rem; background: #ffccd5; }

  /* --- PAGE 2: RULES SCREEN --- */
  #page2 { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .rules-container { max-width: 600px; width: 90%; text-align: left; }
  .rules-container h1 { text-align: center; margin-top: 0; color: #ffccd5; }
  .rules-list { margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  /* --- PAGE 3: TRIVIA GAME ENGINE --- */
  #page3 { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; padding-top: 60px; }
  .top-status-bar { position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 30px; font-size: 1.6rem; letter-spacing: 5px; }
  .game-split-layout { display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; width: 95%; max-width: 950px; gap: 30px; }
  .game-left { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
  .poster-frame { width: 100%; max-width: 280px; aspect-ratio: 1; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); padding: 0; }
  .poster-frame img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .game-right { flex: 2; min-width: 320px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .lyric-box { font-size: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .options-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 15px; width: 100%; }
  .option-box { cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.05rem; padding: 15px; transition: all 0.2s ease; text-align: center; }
  .option-box:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .feedback-section { margin-top: 20px; min-height: 120px; }
  .hint-text { color: #ffccd5; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; animation: shake 0.3s ease; }
  .compliment-box h3 { color: #ffccd5; margin-top: 0; text-align: center; }
  .compliment-box p { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center; }

  /* --- PAGE 4: VIRTUAL BOUQUET BUILDER --- */
  #page4 { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .bouquet-title-box { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .bouquet-title-box h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.2rem; color: #ffccd5; }
  .bouquet-title-box p { margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.9; }
  .builder-split-layout { display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; align-items: stretch; width: 95%; max-width: 950px; gap: 30px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .vase-column { flex: 1; min-width: 320px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
  .vase-canvas { position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 340px; height: 420px; overflow: hidden; }
  .glass-vase {
    position: absolute; bottom: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 120px; height: 160px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); border-radius: 20px 20px 40px 40px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); z-index: 2;
  }
  .glass-vase::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; left: 5px; right: 5px; height: 80px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); border-radius: 0 0 30px 30px; }
  .placed-flower-emoji { position: absolute; font-size: 3.5rem; line-height: 1; user-select: none; animation: dropInFlower 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) forwards; z-index: 1; }
  @keyframes dropInFlower { 0% { transform: translateY(-100px) scale(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0; } 100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1) rotate(var(--rot)); opacity: 1; } }
  .menu-column { flex: 1; min-width: 320px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
  .flower-selection-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; }
  .flower-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; cursor: pointer; padding: 15px 10px; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
  .flower-item:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22); transform: scale(1.04); }
  .flower-item .menu-emoji { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1; }
  .flower-item span { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffccd5; text-align: center; }
  .fortune-cookie-box { min-height: 110px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); color: #fff5f6; }
  .fortune-highlight { color: #ffccd5; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }

  /* --- PAGE 5: PLAYLIST MATRIX CONTAINER --- */
  #page5 { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .playlist-intro-box { max-width: 650px; width: 90%; text-align: center; font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .playlist-intro-box p { margin-bottom: 25px; }
  .playlist-deck { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .playlist-bar { display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 30px; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .playlist-bar:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18); transform: translateX(5px); }
  .track-art-mini { width: 55px; height: 55px; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-right: 18px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .track-art-mini img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .track-meta { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
  .track-title { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #fff5f6; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .track-artist { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #ffccd5; }
  .arrow-btn { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); color: #fff5f6; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25); width: 45px; height: 45px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
  .arrow-btn:hover { background: #fff5f6; color: #800020; transform: scale(1.1); }
  .dedication-panel { display: none; width: 90%; max-width: 600px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .dedication-panel h2 { color: #ffccd5; margin-top: 0; }
  .dedication-panel p { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .dedication-panel .highlight-lyric { font-style: italic; display: block; margin: 15px 0; color: #ffccd5; }

  /* --- 💌 PAGE 6: THE INTERACTIVE ENVELOPE GATE --- */
  #page6 { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
  .envelope-card { max-width: 440px; width: 90%; padding: 40px 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .envelope-card h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #ffccd5; }
  .envelope-wrapper { position: relative; width: 240px; height: 150px; background: #a61c3c; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; overflow: hidden; }
  .envelope-wrapper:hover { transform: scale(1.04) translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
  .envelope-flap { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 120px solid transparent; border-right: 120px solid transparent; border-top: 85px solid #bd2447; z-index: 2; }
  .wax-seal { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -30%); width: 46px; height: 46px; background: radial-gradient(circle, #ffe082 0%, #ffb300 70%, #ffa000 100%); border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), inset 0 1px 2px rgba(255,255,255,0.5); z-index: 3; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #800020; transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
  .envelope-wrapper:hover .wax-seal { transform: translate(-50%, -30%) scale(1.1); }
  .envelope-subtext { margin-top: 25px; font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.7; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* --- 🎀 PAGE 7: THE GRAND FINALE SPLIT SCREEN --- */
  #page7 {
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .p7-left, .p7-right {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 320px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .polaroid-bow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: -12px;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    transform: rotate(-15deg);
    z-index: 10;
    user-select: none;
  }

  /* 📜 STATIONERY CONTAINER FRAME */
  .letter-box-wrapper {
    background: #a61c3c; /* Dark crimson wrap background border frame */
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 95%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .letter-box {
    position: relative;
    background: #eedfc2; /* Exact tan tint from poster background_2.jpg */
    color: #2b2b2b;      
    padding: 45px 30px;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(100, 80, 50, 0.2);
    
    /* Cutout geometry layout */
    clip-path: polygon(
      0% 0%, 5% 2%, 10% 0%, 15% 2%, 20% 0%, 25% 2%, 30% 0%, 35% 2%, 40% 0%, 45% 2%, 50% 0%, 55% 2%, 60% 0%, 65% 2%, 70% 0%, 75% 2%, 80% 0%, 85% 2%, 90% 0%, 95% 2%, 100% 0%,
      100% 100%, 95% 98%, 90% 100%, 85% 98%, 80% 100%, 75% 98%, 70% 100%, 65% 98%, 60% 100%, 55% 98%, 50% 100%, 45% 98%, 40% 100%, 35% 98%, 30% 100%, 25% 98%, 20% 100%, 15% 98%, 10% 100%, 5% 98%, 0% 100%
    );
  }

  /* 💋 BACKGROUND LIPSTICK KISSES */
  .letter-box::before {
    content: '💋';
    position: absolute;
    top: 15%; left: 10%;
    font-size: 1.8rem; opacity: 0.35; transform: rotate(-15deg);
  }
  .letter-box::after {
    content: '💋';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 8%; right: 12%;
    font-size: 1.9rem; opacity: 0.4; transform: rotate(20deg);
  }
  
  .extra-kiss-1 { position: absolute; top: 42%; left: 8%; font-size: 1.6rem; opacity: 0.3; transform: rotate(10deg); }
  .extra-kiss-2 { position: absolute; bottom: 35%; right: 6%; font-size: 1.7rem; opacity: 0.35; transform: rotate(-25deg); }

  /* ✒️ TYPOGRAPHY ENGINE CONFIGURATION RULES */
  .letter-header-happy {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .letter-header-title {
    font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    color: #800020; 
    margin: -5px 0 25px 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .letter-body-content {
    font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
    font-size: 1.65rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: left;
    color: #333333;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    word-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .letter-signature {
    font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    color: #800020;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  /* --- CORE EFFECT EXTENSIONS --- */
  .cracker { position: fixed; pointer-events: none; font-size: 30px; animation: burst 2s ease-out forwards; z-index: 9999; }
  @keyframes burst { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: translate(var(--mx), var(--my)) scale(0.5); opacity: 0; } }
  @keyframes shake { 0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); } 25% { transform: translateX(-6px); } 75% { transform: translateX(6px); } }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .game-split-layout, .builder-split-layout, #page7 { flex-direction: column; }
    .options-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .top-status-bar { top: 10px; right: 10px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .vase-canvas { height: 340px; }
    .letter-body-content { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="page1" class="page active">
  <div class="p1-left"><div class="glass-polaroid"><img src="main.jpg" alt="Welcome Cutie"></div></div>
  <div class="p1-right">
    <div class="lock-screen-title"> My Sahiba🌹</div>
    <div class="lock-screen-subtitle">Enter the secret code to step inside...</div>
    <div id="passcodeDisplay" class="passcode-display"></div>
    <div class="keypad">
      <button class="key" onclick="pressNum('1')">1</button><button class="key" onclick="pressNum('2')">2</button><button class="key" onclick="pressNum('3')">3</button>
      <button class="key" onclick="pressNum('4')">4</button><button class="key" onclick="pressNum('5')">5</button><button class="key" onclick="pressNum('6')">6</button>
      <button class="key" onclick="pressNum('7')">7</button><button class="key" onclick="pressNum('8')">8</button><button class="key" onclick="pressNum('9')">9</button>
      <button class="key action-key" onclick="clearPass()">Clear</button><button class="key" onclick="pressNum('0')">0</button><button class="key action-key" onclick="checkPass()">OK</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="page2" class="page">
  <div class="glass-box rules-container">
    <h1>Guess The Song Name For A Surprise ✨</h1>
    <ol class="rules-list">
      <li>You have three hearts. One wrong answer and it will cost you a heart! ❤️❌</li>
      <li>Choosing a right ans will give u a compliment as i always do hehe 😉</li>
      <li>If u give the answer wrong ull get a hint on screen itself.</li>
      <li>No cheating or help from Spotify, YouTube, or any other streaming platform will be tolerated! 😤</li>
    </ol>
    <button class="play-btn" onclick="navigateTo('page3'); initGame();">Play Game 🎶</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="page3" class="page">
  <div class="top-status-bar" id="heartsContainer">❤️❤️❤️</div>
  <div class="game-split-layout">
    <div class="game-left"><div class="glass-box poster-frame"><img id="posterDisplay" src="1.jpg" alt="Song Hint Poster"></div></div>
    <div class="game-right">
      <div class="glass-box lyric-box" id="questionDisplay">Loading lyric...</div>
      <div class="options-grid" id="optionsContainer"></div>
      <div class="feedback-section" id="feedbackDisplay"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="page4" class="page">
  <div class="trivia-wrapper" style="max-width:950px; margin-top:0;">
    <div class="bouquet-title-box">
      <h1>Great job my Sahiba! 🌸✨</h1>
      <p>Tap your favorite flowers to build your custom arrangement inside the vase!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="builder-split-layout">
      <div class="vase-column"><div class="glass-box vase-canvas" id="vaseCanvas"><div class="glass-vase"></div></div></div>
      <div class="menu-column">
        <div class="glass-box flower-selection-grid">
          <div class="glass-box flower-item" onclick="addFlowerToVase('rose', '🌹')"><div class="menu-emoji">🌹</div><span>Rose</span></div>
          <div class="glass-box flower-item" onclick="addFlowerToVase('tulip', '🌷')"><div class="menu-emoji">🌷</div><span>Tulip</span></div>
          <div class="glass-box flower-item" onclick="addFlowerToVase('daisy', '🌼')"><div class="menu-emoji">🌼</div><span>Daisy</span></div>
          <div class="glass-box flower-item" onclick="addFlowerToVase('lily', '💮')"><div class="menu-emoji">💮</div><span>Lily</span></div>
          <div class="glass-box flower-item" onclick="addFlowerToVase('sunflower', '🌻')"><div class="menu-emoji">🌻</div><span>Sunflower</span></div>
          <div class="glass-box flower-item" onclick="addFlowerToVase('lavender', '🪻')"><div class="menu-emoji">🪻</div><span>Lavender</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-box fortune-cookie-box" id="fortuneDisplay"><span style="opacity:0.7;">Click a flower above to open a sweet note... 🥠💌</span></div>
        <div id="deliveryContainer" style="display:none; width:100%;"><button class="action-btn" onclick="navigateTo('page5')" style="margin-top:10px; background:#ffccd5; color:#800020;">Deliver Bouquet 🚚💝</button></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="page5" class="page">
  <div class="glass-box playlist-intro-box" id="musicGate">
    <p>"Although for many Music is just a thing to vibe by, for me Music is love and there are multiple songs whenever i listen to them i think abt YOU My Sahiba!!"</p>
    <button class="play-btn" onclick="openPlaylistDeck()">Dive into Music 🎧</button>
  </div>

  <div class="playlist-deck" id="playlistDeck">
    <div class="glass-box playlist-bar">
      <div class="track-art-mini"><img src="a1.jpg" alt="Track 1"></div>
      <div class="track-meta"><span class="track-title">Make You Mine</span><span class="track-artist">Public</span></div>
      <button class="arrow-btn" onclick="openDedication(1)">➡️</button>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-box playlist-bar">
      <div class="track-art-mini"><img src="a2.jpg" alt="Track 2"></div>
      <div class="track-meta"><span class="track-title">The Shade</span><span class="track-artist">Rex Orange County</span></div>
      <button class="arrow-btn" onclick="openDedication(2)">➡️</button>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-box playlist-bar">
      <div class="track-art-mini"><img src="a3.jpg" alt="Track 3"></div>
      <div class="track-meta"><span class="track-title">About You</span><span class="track-artist">The 1975</span></div>
      <button class="arrow-btn" onclick="openDedication(3)">➡️</button>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-box playlist-bar">
      <div class="track-art-mini"><img src="a4.jpg" alt="Track 4"></div>
      <div class="track-meta"><span class="track-title">Be My Baby</span><span class="track-artist">The Ronettes</span></div>
      <button class="arrow-btn" onclick="openDedication(4)">➡️</button>
    </div>
